   FOR IMMEDIATE RELEASE
   November 28, 2001
   (Updated January 9, 2002)

   IMPORTANT NOTICE ABOUT US POSTAL SERVICE MAIL DELIVERY

   The delivery of first class mail to IMLS has been delayed since
   mid-October and delays are expected to continue for the foreseeable
   future. Please consider using alternatives, such as e-mail, fax, or
   commercial delivery services. If you are concerned about the status of
   any time-sensitive mail, please contact the relevant individual or
   program to ensure your materials arrived. Every attempt is being made
   to accommodate late arriving mail. We appreciate your patience. Please
   contact us if you have any questions.

   Special Notice to Grant applicants: Due to the length and number of
   copies required for complete submission, applications cannot be
   accepted by fax or e-mail. MAP applicants are encouraged to call AAM at
   (202) 289-9118.

